data.description: Everything is new! Cozy small farmhouse feel with plenty of backyard and new garage space. New 25 yr roof, new flooring, new stone and plush carpeting, A/C approx 5 yrs old, new copper wiring, new addition *Bonus room, remodeled kitchen with granite, new higher end appliances, gas kitchen stove, self closing cabinet doors, farmhouse sink, kitchen island. Bathroom completely updated with new fixtures and recessed lighting. Motion detection front lighting, epoxy speckled garage floor. Smoke detectors in every room*Premium blinds*Outside lights automatically turn on when sun goes down*Carbon Monoxide detector in kitchen & hallway. Fluorescent lights in closets. Move right in with no worries! Age restricted community w/ NO HOA monthly fees, tons of amenities, pools, recreational activities
